# /exit — Dame Luthas session teardown

**CORTEX close is mandatory.** Follow `documentation-standards/skills/exit/SKILL.md`.

## Step 0: CORTEX prime end

From repo root — session id from `.cortex-boot.json` → `_meta.sessionId`:

```bash
npx tsx ../.agent-kb/anvil/run.mts close --session=sess_... --repo=dame-luthas-app
npx tsx ../.agent-kb/db/sync.mts --push
```

## Step 1: Quality gates

```bash
npx tsc --noEmit && npm run lint && npm run build
npm run ci:parity
```

## Step 2: Checkpoint + manifest

```bash
npx tsx scripts/checkpoint.mts "session-title"
```

Manifest: `documentation-standards/docs/context-manifests/YYYY-MM-DD_dame-luthas-*.md`

## Step 3: Slack handoff

```bash
cd ../documentation-standards
node scripts/post-handoff-to-slack.mjs --file docs/context-manifests/<manifest>.md --kind handoff
```

## Step 4: 40x verify

```bash
cd ../documentation-standards
node scripts/verify-workspace-40x.mjs
```
